		<article class="article" data-post-id="999976" data-post-url="https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/03/27/hun-sen-khmer-cambodia-leaders-line-up-coronavirus-scapegoat/" data-lfcollectionmeta="eyJ0eXAiOiJqd3QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..5NMil-6uxNh-Q8L2TpKnhdT2tt9EEgqEIPmmHHJYP3A" data-lfchecksum="56544043d37ebbc2d4a3742a744d5b9a" data-lfarticleid="foreignpolicy_wp_999976">

			
				


<a
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/category/analysis/argument/"
    class="department-name">
    <h3 class="department">Argument</h3></a>
<span
    class="hed-heading"
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/03/27/hun-sen-khmer-cambodia-leaders-line-up-coronavirus-scapegoat/">
    <h1 class="hed">Cambodia’s Leaders Line Up a Coronavirus Scapegoat</h1>
</span>
<h2 class="dek-heading">Hun Sen needs somebody to blame for the impending disaster. </h2>
<div class="meta-data ">
    <address class="author-list">
    <span class="pre">By</span>
    <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/author/david-hutt/"
        rel="author"
        class="author">
    David Hutt</a></address>
    <span class="separator">|</span>
    <time
    pubdate
    datetime="2020-03-27"
    title="March 27th, 2020"
    class="date-time">
March 27, 2020, 5:40 PM</time>
</div>




				<figure class="figure-image ">
            <span
            style="padding-bottom:66.666666666667%;
        "
                class="image-attachment -ratioscale  horizontal-orientation">
        <img
            data-sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
            data-srcset="https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1207986922.jpg?quality=90 1500w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1207986922.jpg?resize=150,100&amp;quality=90 150w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1207986922.jpg?resize=550,367&amp;quality=90 550w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1207986922.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=90 768w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1207986922.jpg?resize=400,267&amp;quality=90 400w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1207986922.jpg?resize=401,267&amp;quality=90 401w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1207986922.jpg?resize=800,533&amp;quality=90 800w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1207986922.jpg?resize=275,183&amp;quality=90 275w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1207986922.jpg?resize=325,217&amp;quality=90 325w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1207986922.jpg?resize=600,400&amp;quality=90 600w"
