				<div>
					<b>EDITOR’S NOTE:</b> We’re making some of our coronavirus pandemic coverage free for nonsubscribers. You can read those articles <a href="https://foreignpolicy.com/projects/essential-coronavirus-reading-now-free-for-everyone/">here</a>. You can also listen to our weekly coronavirus podcast, <a href="https://foreignpolicy.com/podcasts/dont-touch-your-face-coronavirus-podcast/">Don’t Touch Your Face</a>, and subscribe to our newsletters <a href="https://foreignpolicy.com/newsletters/">here</a>.
